# 🏗️ Core Engineering Concepts

Notes:
* Queue ➔ First-In-First-Out (FIFO) pipeline. Main thread se heavy tasks offload karne ke liye use hota hai.
* BullMQ ➔ Task scheduler engine jo multi-concurrency aur background scaling support karta hai.
* Redis ➔ System storage state database. Saari pending, delayed, aur active jobs memory me hold rakhta hai.

```text
[ Express Request ] ➔ [ Controller ] ➔ [ Producer ] ➔ [ Queue (Redis) ] ➔ [ Worker (Traffic Police) ] ➔ [ Registry Router ] ➔ [ Job Handler ] ➔ [ Nodemailer Service ]
```

