# ❌ Critical Debug Ledger (Common Mistakes)

[x] Mistake: Setting worker concurrency too high (`concurrency: 50`) using a free Gmail SMTP pool. Gmail blocks the socket pipeline immediately due to spam rules (`Rate Limit Exceeded`).
[√] Fix: Keep development concurrency strict between `2` to `5` parallel jobs via env variables.

[x] Mistake: Forgetting to export the worker instantiation. The thread pool never registers a background listener on node engine bootstrap sequence.
[√] Fix: Create a module bridge entry file `src/modules/email/index.ts` to export all systems uniformly.







